title: Snack
alt: Although grad students, suddenly reminded that food exists, tend to just grab and devour both without further discussion.
transcript:
[Ponytail, with a cookie in one hand and an apple in the other, approaches an alarmed Cueball.]
 Ponytail: Hey, do you want a cookie? Or an apple?
 Cueball: Who are you!? Did the IRB approve this!? Is everyone here an actor!? [Caption under the panel:]
 The best prank you can play on Psych majors is just to offer them a snack.
